Package: transform
Title: Easy variable transformations in R
Version: 0.2.3
Authors@R: person("Derek", "Damron", email = "damrondm@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: transform provides lightweight and robust functions for common
    variable transformations. Transformations supported include trimming and
    rescaling for numeric variables, regrouping for categorical variables, and
    imputing for both numeric and categorical variables.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Suggests:
    devtools,
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    pander
License: file LICENSE
LazyData: true
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports:
    Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
